<h4 class="heading"><span class="type">Paragraph</span></h4>
<p>Consider the following projectile launched from the origin, with an initial velocity of <span class="process-math">\(v_0\)</span> and angle of elevation <span class="process-math">\(\theta\text{.}\)</span> <div class="image-box" style="width: 75%; margin-left: 12.5%; margin-right: 12.5%;"><img src="external/frog.jpg" class="contained" alt="Path of a thrown object."></div> Assuming that there is no air resistance and the acceleration due to gravity is <span class="process-math">\(-g\text{.}\)</span></p>
